<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/homepage.css" />

<div class="mx-auto grid grid-rows-[70px,_minmax(0,_1fr)] h-full p-5">

  <h2 class="font-bold text-3xl mb-5">Welcome, {{first_name}}!</h2>

  <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-5">
    <div
      class="grid grid-rows-[50px,_minmax(0,_1fr),_30px] p-3 w-full sm:w-1/3 sm:max-w-[400px] border-2 border-black"
    >
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mt-3">Characters</h3>
      <div
        id="characters"
        class="grid grid-rows-[min-content,_40px,_minmax(0,_1fr)] mt-3 h-full overflow-hidden"
      >
        <a class="text-center w-full" type="submit" href="/create">Create a
          Character</a>
        <img class="-mt-1 mb-12" src="/images/underline.png" alt="" />

        {{! CHARACTER LIST }}
        <div
          id="character-list"
          class="grid auto-rows-min gap-1 w-full h-full overflow-auto"
        >
          {{#if characters.length}}
            {{#each characters as |character|}}
              <button
                class="text-xl py-3 px-5 hover:scale-[1.02] bg-transparent transition-all"
                data-id="{{character.id}}"
                data-name="{{character.character_name}}"
                data-avatar="{{character.avatar}}"
                data-class="{{character.class.class_name}}"
                data-race="{{character.race.race_name}}"
              >
                {{character.character_name}}
              </button>
            {{/each}}
          {{/if}}
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative mt-3">

        <img
          class="absolute bottom-0 w-full"
          src="/images/underline.png"
          alt=""
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <section
      class="relative grid grid-rows-[min-content,_minmax(0,_1fr),_min-content] flex-grow border-black border-2 p-5"
    >
      {{! PREVIEW HEADER }}
      <div class="">
        <div class="flex">
          {{! NAME and CLASS }}
          <div class="w-1/2">
            <h2 class="text-4xl"><span id="selected-character-name"></span></h2>
            <h2>Race:
              <span id="selected-character-race"></span>
            </h2>
            <h2>Class:
              <span id="selected-character-class"></span>
            </h2>
          </div>
          {{! IMAGE }}
          <img
            class="w-1/2 aspect-square object-cover"
            id="selected-character-avatar"
            src=""
            alt=""
          />
        </div>
        <div>
          {{#if attributes.length}}
            {{#each attributes as |attribute|}}
              <p>{{attribute.name}}:
                <span
                  id="selected-character-attribute-{{attribute.id}}"
                ></span></p>
            {{/each}}
          {{/if}}
        </div>

      </div>

      {{! SCROLLABLE BODY }}
      <div
        id="selected-character-description"
        class="h-full overflow-auto border-2 border-black"
      >
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit, amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Porro
        inventore, amet, expedita, reiciendis aliquam similique libero quas enim
        sequi odio aspernatur? Minima deleniti eum laudantium voluptatum
        molestias veritatis repellat! Eligendi a ipsam est et voluptas unde
        excepturi cum harum, ab maiores tenetur cumque magnam alias voluptatibus
        culpa quod! Quae, cupiditate? Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur
        adipisicing elit. Tempore eaque nulla est hic? Corporis, libero quod!
        Aspernatur eveniet earum adipisci similique aut praesentium id nulla
        perspiciatis repudiandae nihil aliquam voluptatibus ullam, excepturi,
        molestias impedit doloribus vero ducimus quia, provident non!
        Dignissimos culpa quo ad, eaque ipsam dicta consequatur tempore esse
        nihil et soluta non repellendus illo. Dolorem unde, atque, eum soluta ab
        odit culpa corrupti provident ducimus tenetur minima! Et repellat
        provident veniam obcaecati hic labore aliquam eum numquam eaque, sit
        nobis mollitia voluptatem placeat aperiam, odit voluptates sed modi
        laudantium sequi minus! Architecto minima veritatis eligendi nisi.
        Dicta, facere.
      </div>
      {{! BUTTONS }}
      <div class="flex">
        <a id="selected-character-edit" class="" href="#">Edit</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

</div>

<script src="/js/homepage.js"></script>